  "title": "CHEF DE CUISINE",
  "description": "<p><strong>SOFRA TURKISH CAFÉ &amp; RESTAURANT</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for Turkish Cruisine chef to join our Kitchen team.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Knowledge of Turkish and Mediterranean Cruisine.</li>\n  <li>Ability to teach fellow chef, team-players.</li>\n  <li>Good customer service skills, the ability to work flexible hours, and at least six months of kitchen experience are preferred.</li>\n  <li>Interpersonal skills – must interact with other chefs, management, and kitchen staff to receive instructions, feedback, and assistance.</li>\n  <li>Reading skills – the ability to read and comprehend well is necessary</li>\n  <li>Flexibility <strong>– </strong>may be required to work alternating shifts, weekends, and holidays.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Others:</p>\n<p>- Career advancement prospects</p>\n<p>- Good working environment</p>\n<p>- Salaries will commensurate with qualifications and experience</p>\n<p>- Location: Town</p>\n<p>- Knowledge of Turkish Language</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Qualified or interested candidates, please send your updated resume in WORDS format,</p>\n<p>stating the following :-</p>\n<p>- Availability</p>\n<p>- Current / last drawn salaries</p>\n<p>- Reasons for leaving previous employment</p>\n<p>- Expected Salary</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
